---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const rawBase = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const base = rawBase.endsWith('/') ? rawBase : rawBase + '/';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home" description="Aperto - A fresh Bible translation that welcomes everyone to the conversation">
  <section class="hero min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl mb-8 tracking-tight logo" style="color: var(--color-headline);">aperto</h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12" style="color: #5A5A5A;">
        A fresh translation that welcomes everyone to the conversation—whether you're deeply rooted in faith, exploring from the outside, or somewhere in between.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
        <a href={`${base}en/luke/1`} class="px-8 py-4 rounded font-medium transition-all hover:opacity-90" style="background-color: #8B7355; color: #FFFBF5;">
          Read Luke 1 (English)
        </a>
        <a href={`${base}de/luke/1`} class="px-8 py-4 rounded font-medium transition-all border-2 hover:opacity-80" style="border-color: #8B7355; color: #8B7355;">
          Lukas 1 (Deutsch)
        </a>
        <a href={`${base}fr/luke/1`} class="px-8 py-4 rounded font-medium transition-all border-2 hover:opacity-80" style="border-color: #8B7355; color: #8B7355;">
          Luc 1 (Français)
        </a>
        <a href={`${base}pl/luke/1`} class="px-8 py-4 rounded font-medium transition-all border-2 hover:opacity-80" style="border-color: #8B7355; color: #8B7355;">
          Łukasz 1 (Polski)
        </a>
        <a href={`${base}tr/luke/1`} class="px-8 py-4 rounded font-medium transition-all border-2 hover:opacity-80" style="border-color: #8B7355; color: #8B7355;">
          Luka 1 (Türkçe)
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24" style="background-color: rgba(245, 230, 220, 0.3);">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-12 text-center headline-mixed">A Different Kind of Bible</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-3">Accessible</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: #6A6A6A;">
            Contemporary language that reads like modern literature. No jargon, no insider vocabulary—just the text, alive and direct.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-3">Multimedia</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: #6A6A6A;">
            Audio Bible, podcasts, original songs, and spiritual practices. Experience the text in the way that resonates with you.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-3">Open Source</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: #6A6A6A;">
            CC BY-SA 4.0 license. Free to share, adapt, and build upon. Available in multiple languages.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-8 headline-mixed">Start Reading</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12" style="color: #6A6A6A;">
        We begin with Luke Chapter 1: the announcement of John the Baptist, the angel Gabriel visiting Mary, and two revolutionary songs that still echo today.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <a href={`${base}en/luke/1`} class="p-6 rounded-lg transition-all hover:shadow-lg group" style="background-color: #FFFBF5; border: 1px solid #F5E6DC;">
          <span class="text-xl">Luke 1</span>
          <span class="block text-sm mt-1" style="color: #9A8F85;">English</span>
        </a>
        <a href={`${base}de/luke/1`} class="p-6 rounded-lg transition-all hover:shadow-lg group" style="background-color: #FFFBF5; border: 1px solid #F5E6DC;">
          <span class="text-xl">Lukas 1</span>
          <span class="block text-sm mt-1" style="color: #9A8F85;">Deutsch</span>
        </a>
        <a href={`${base}fr/luke/1`} class="p-6 rounded-lg transition-all hover:shadow-lg group" style="background-color: #FFFBF5; border: 1px solid #F5E6DC;">
          <span class="text-xl">Luc 1</span>
          <span class="block text-sm mt-1" style="color: #9A8F85;">Français</span>
        </a>
        <a href={`${base}pl/luke/1`} class="p-6 rounded-lg transition-all hover:shadow-lg group" style="background-color: #FFFBF5; border: 1px solid #F5E6DC;">
          <span class="text-xl">Łukasz 1</span>
          <span class="block text-sm mt-1" style="color: #9A8F85;">Polski</span>
        </a>
        <a href={`${base}tr/luke/1`} class="p-6 rounded-lg transition-all hover:shadow-lg group" style="background-color: #FFFBF5; border: 1px solid #F5E6DC;">
          <span class="text-xl">Luka 1</span>
          <span class="block text-sm mt-1" style="color: #9A8F85;">Türkçe</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
